# Trivy ignore file for the pulse-server image and fs scans.
#
# Escape hatch for the CI gates in server-ci.yml (image scan) and security.yml
# (fs scan): when a CRITICAL/HIGH CVE has an upstream fix that is not yet
# available in our pinned base image, add it here so unrelated PRs can merge.
#
# Every entry MUST carry a justification and an expiry, e.g.:
#   # CVE-2026-12345 — fixed upstream, waiting for python:3.11-slim rebuild;
#   # remove by 2026-07-01
#   CVE-2026-12345 exp:2026-07-01
#
# Keep this file empty in the steady state.
